1
00:01:42,200 --> 00:01:44,160
Jinbe came to help?!

2
00:01:44,160 --> 00:01:46,870
Yeah, I was surprised too.

3
00:01:47,730 --> 00:01:51,530
That's a relief. So Nami-san is okay...

4
00:01:54,380 --> 00:01:58,540
But now, we need to figure out how to meet up with them.

5
00:01:58,540 --> 00:02:02,640
Once they hear you're coming back,
I'm sure they'll be happy.

6
00:02:11,700 --> 00:02:12,860
Goodbye!

7
00:02:13,500 --> 00:02:14,320
Sorry...

8
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:16,530
we should never have done this!

9
00:02:17,450 --> 00:02:21,720
I'm too ashamed to face Nami-san...

10
00:02:23,520 --> 00:02:28,120
Nami and the others were so worried about you.

11
00:02:28,860 --> 00:02:32,620
And yet, I put them through this terrifying ordeal...

12
00:02:37,630 --> 00:02:39,970
Oh, the rain is stopping.

13
00:03:03,030 --> 00:03:04,530
I found it!

14
00:03:04,530 --> 00:03:07,640
You sure?! Chobro!

15
00:03:08,410 --> 00:03:12,250
Do you think they can hear us
through this piece of glass?

16
00:03:12,250 --> 00:03:19,050
The last mirror piece I used to talk to you guys broke on the head of that tree monster, Kingbaum.

17
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:23,970
It broke!

18
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:27,390
So...

19
00:03:28,350 --> 00:03:33,150
There should be at least a piece of glass
that connects to this one.

20
00:03:35,610 --> 00:03:38,610
Hey! Luffy!

21
00:03:38,610 --> 00:03:40,400
Hey!

22
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:42,660
Luffy!

23
00:03:44,570 --> 00:03:48,280
Are you there, Luffy?!

24
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,590
Is that...?

25
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,130
It's Chopper!

26
00:03:51,660 --> 00:03:54,250
Hey!

27
00:03:54,250 --> 00:03:57,540
Answer me if you're there!

28
00:03:57,540 --> 00:03:59,550
Chopper!

29
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:02,260
Luffy!

30
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:04,470
Hey!

31
00:04:06,260 --> 00:04:09,390
Luffy! Can you hear me?!

32
00:04:09,390 --> 00:04:11,560
Hey!

33
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:13,040
Here it is!

34
00:04:13,550 --> 00:04:16,440
This is it! It's a piece of glass!

35
00:04:16,440 --> 00:04:18,190
Can you hear me?!

36
00:04:18,190 --> 00:04:20,570
Why is his voice coming out of a mirror?

37
00:04:20,570 --> 00:04:25,490
It's a long story, but Chopper and the others
are in a mirror dimension.

38
00:04:26,490 --> 00:04:28,740
Are you okay, Chopper?

39
00:04:28,740 --> 00:04:32,960
Oh, Luffy! Thank goodness! You're really there!

40
00:04:34,580 --> 00:04:37,130
Luffy! Is Sanji-kun there too?!

41
00:04:38,250 --> 00:04:40,670
Yeah, he's here!

42
00:04:41,540 --> 00:04:44,880
Sanji-san, I'm glad that you're okay.

43
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:50,720
How are you guys?

44
00:04:50,720 --> 00:04:56,150
We saved everybody from
inside the mirror, Luffy!

45
00:04:56,150 --> 00:05:00,440
Brook even got copies of the poneglyphs!

46
00:05:00,440 --> 00:05:01,780
Really?!

47
00:05:01,780 --> 00:05:04,360
I'm impressed with you guys!

48
00:05:04,360 --> 00:05:09,580
Y-Your compliment doesn't make me happy, you fool!

49
00:05:11,160 --> 00:05:12,690
You fool!

50
00:05:13,680 --> 00:05:15,620
You silly little goose!

51
00:05:16,460 --> 00:05:21,750
Luffy, it's good that Sanji's there,
but did you two come to an agreement?

52
00:05:30,390 --> 00:05:33,560
Sanji isn't... coming back yet.

53
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:36,270
What?!

54
00:05:51,120 --> 00:05:53,910
Listen, everyone.

55
00:05:53,910 --> 00:05:58,200
We're gonna crash Big Mom's tea party and the wedding.

56
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:01,000
And we're gonna save Sanji's family!

57
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:04,380
And then, Sanji will leave with us!

58
00:06:10,170 --> 00:06:13,560
B... Big...

59
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:23,480
Luffy! She's an emperor!

60
00:06:25,030 --> 00:06:30,280
I don't want to risk everyone's...
I mean, Nami-san's life over my own personal issues!

61
00:06:30,740 --> 00:06:31,700
So...

62
00:06:39,330 --> 00:06:42,250
Yay!

63
00:06:46,340 --> 00:06:48,050
Damn you!

64
00:06:48,050 --> 00:06:53,970
I heard you and Luffy got into a big fight,
so I was worried, you idiot!

65
00:06:53,970 --> 00:06:58,350
I'm so relieved! Really, you idiot!

66
00:06:58,350 --> 00:07:00,980
You big idiot!

67
00:07:00,980 --> 00:07:05,480
If we do that, then Sanji-kun will
leave with us, right, Luffy?!

68
00:07:09,860 --> 00:07:12,450
Nami-san... I...

69
00:07:12,450 --> 00:07:15,080
Oh, Sanji-kun.

70
00:07:15,080 --> 00:07:19,500
For scaring me like you did...

71
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,540
I will never forgive you!

72
00:07:27,540 --> 00:07:28,710
Nami...

73
00:07:32,860 --> 00:07:37,520
But we can talk about that later.
The tea party is soon.

74
00:07:37,520 --> 00:07:41,480
I'm gonna help bring you back no matter what, Sanji-kun!

75
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:47,080
What?! Are you proposing to me, Nami-san ?!

76
00:07:47,080 --> 00:07:50,150
I don't know why, but I think you're fine now.

77
00:07:52,920 --> 00:07:56,660
Alright, Luffy, we know what we need to do now.

78
00:07:56,660 --> 00:07:57,820
Yeah.

79
00:07:57,820 --> 00:08:02,750
By the way, Sanji's sister saved my life.

80
00:08:11,020 --> 00:08:13,090
So I wanna save them all.

81
00:08:13,090 --> 00:08:15,720
Yes, let's save them all.

82
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:18,930
But it will not be easy.

83
00:08:18,930 --> 00:08:22,390
Even though we're not aiming
to take Big Mom down,

84
00:08:22,390 --> 00:08:26,940
she always looks forward to
her tea parties.

85
00:08:26,940 --> 00:08:33,030
By crashing it,
we'll unleash the wrath of an emperor.

86
00:08:36,660 --> 00:08:43,120
On top of that, while I'm sure you've faced a number of Big Mom's ministers,

87
00:08:43,880 --> 00:08:48,210
they are merely the tip of the iceberg of her forces.

88
00:08:48,210 --> 00:08:52,380
The figures attending the tea party
will be even more fearsome.

89
00:08:54,880 --> 00:09:00,720
Not to mention her invited guests from around the world, the kingpins of the underworld.

90
00:09:00,720 --> 00:09:03,850
We, on the other hand...

91
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:10,990
Have 10 people in total.

92
00:09:10,990 --> 00:09:14,200
Hey! We're not part of this!

93
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:17,070
Don't round up!
There are only eight of you!

94
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:19,490
I hope they slaughter you!

95
00:09:21,370 --> 00:09:22,580
Luffy.

96
00:09:23,330 --> 00:09:26,500
I've already told everyone here,

97
00:09:26,500 --> 00:09:30,300
but I need to tell you about something else.

98
00:09:31,300 --> 00:09:35,260
Have you ever heard of Capone "Gang" Bege?

99
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:38,220
Yeah, he's the guy who took Sanji away.

100
00:09:40,810 --> 00:09:45,230
He's one of the Worst Generation,
with a name as infamous as yours.

101
00:09:45,230 --> 00:09:50,520
He hails from the West Blue,
where there are five powerful mafia familes.

102
00:09:50,520 --> 00:09:53,730
They control the underworld.

103
00:09:53,730 --> 00:09:58,970
They are known as the Five Families of the West, and one of those bosses,

104
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:01,040
is "Gang" Bege.

105
00:10:01,640 --> 00:10:08,420
He was given his "Gang" epithet when he was young.
He used to be a notorious hitman.

106
00:10:08,420 --> 00:10:10,460
A hitman...

107
00:10:10,460 --> 00:10:15,710
I heard he was a sick young man
who cut the heads off helpless creatures

108
00:10:15,710 --> 00:10:21,670
and took joy watching them in the throes of death.

109
00:10:22,600 --> 00:10:24,850
What kind of awful person would...?

110
00:10:24,850 --> 00:10:28,980
Now imagine that happening to an organization.

111
00:10:35,190 --> 00:10:37,760
How does it taste?

112
00:10:37,760 --> 00:10:40,240
I wish it were more bitter.

113
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,660
Then, how about this?

114
00:10:45,040 --> 00:10:45,740
Boss!

115
00:10:48,580 --> 00:10:50,600
You little...

116
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:55,790
The lead tastes bitter, doesn't it?

117
00:10:58,560 --> 00:11:03,470
In his days as a young gangster,
he only killed the leaders of criminal organizations.

118
00:11:03,470 --> 00:11:09,190
And when he became the leader of his own family,
he continued to only kill rival bosses.

119
00:11:12,730 --> 00:11:13,610
Bege?

120
00:11:14,380 --> 00:11:16,110
Don't resist.

121
00:11:16,110 --> 00:11:18,320
What? Are you betraying me?!

122
00:11:20,280 --> 00:11:22,180
You're outnumbered!

123
00:11:22,180 --> 00:11:23,530
Bege!

124
00:11:28,410 --> 00:11:30,330
But Bege...

125
00:11:30,330 --> 00:11:34,340
never showed interest
in his enemy's position or territory.

126
00:11:34,340 --> 00:11:36,290
He merely took their valuables and left.

127
00:11:36,290 --> 00:11:38,790
"Bloody Tragedy! An Internal Feud?!"

128
00:11:38,790 --> 00:11:41,260
"Waking Nightmare! Underworld Remains Tense"

129
00:11:41,260 --> 00:11:43,720
"The Underworld Society in Chaos! Triggered by the Assassination?"

130
00:11:47,560 --> 00:11:52,070
Afterward, he would enjoy watching
 the violent power struggles within the groups

131
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:56,570
and the confusion of their allied syndicates.

132
00:11:57,110 --> 00:11:59,860
He is truly a tasteless man.

133
00:11:59,860 --> 00:12:03,990
But in this world, what goes around comes around.

134
00:12:03,990 --> 00:12:09,370
He is now targeted constantly
by those seeking vengeance.

135
00:12:13,370 --> 00:12:14,630
However,

136
00:12:14,630 --> 00:12:21,070
Bege treats that like a game.
He uses his iron fortress to fight them off,

137
00:12:21,070 --> 00:12:24,300
and mocks the weakness of his enemies.

138
00:12:24,300 --> 00:12:29,180
When he got tired of being on land,
he went out to sea and carried on his own ways.

139
00:12:30,000 --> 00:12:31,430
Boss!

140
00:12:31,430 --> 00:12:35,230
Who did this?! Damn!

141
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:41,150
He's made his name by taking out pirate captains.
Only the pirate captains.

142
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:51,660
Even at sea, he is plagued
by enemies seeking revenge...

143
00:12:52,520 --> 00:12:53,410
So, working for an emperor
is his perfect safe haven.

144
00:12:53,410 --> 00:12:56,600
So, working for an emperor
is his perfect safe haven.

145
00:12:56,600 --> 00:12:59,380
That's why he decided to ally with Big Mom.

146
00:13:01,670 --> 00:13:07,110
Because Big Mom thought highly of his sharpened
sense of vigilance and incredible defensive ability,

147
00:13:07,110 --> 00:13:12,490
he was granted the title of rook
just before the upcoming tea party,

148
00:13:12,490 --> 00:13:16,400
and placed in charge of security for the entire event.

149
00:13:16,400 --> 00:13:20,650
Why are you telling us this now, Jinbe?

150
00:13:20,650 --> 00:13:26,110
If they are the security guards,
nobody can stop them from achieving their goal.

151
00:13:26,110 --> 00:13:26,950
Huh?

152
00:13:26,950 --> 00:13:31,370
The main event of this tea party is the wedding.

153
00:13:31,370 --> 00:13:37,500
As you are now aware, Big Mom intends to slaughter the Vinsmokes during the ceremony,

154
00:13:37,500 --> 00:13:41,380
and then acquire the remnants of Germa for herself.

155
00:13:41,380 --> 00:13:46,430
But meanwhile, behind her back,
 Bege has his own plan to take Big Mom's head.

156
00:13:46,430 --> 00:13:47,590
What?!

157
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:51,010
What the hell is going on?!
Everyone is planning their own conspiracies!

158
00:13:53,350 --> 00:13:58,880
Luffy, I'm sure you remember that Pekoms was the one who guided you here.

159
00:13:58,880 --> 00:14:01,820
He was kidnapped by Bege,

160
00:14:01,820 --> 00:14:06,030
and they tried to get him to cooperate with their plan.

161
00:14:06,760 --> 00:14:10,240
Pekoms... So that's where he went...

162
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:24,590
Pekoms is loyal, so he refused. In order to keep him
quiet, Bege shot him off a cliff into a swarm of sharks.

163
00:14:28,630 --> 00:14:30,720
What?!

164
00:14:36,770 --> 00:14:38,270
But...

165
00:14:38,270 --> 00:14:44,070
my companions were watching
and saved him just in time.

166
00:14:44,100 --> 00:14:46,570
He's currently recuperating.

167
00:14:46,570 --> 00:14:49,310
Thank goodness! He's okay!

168
00:14:49,310 --> 00:14:52,450
He's been through a lot.

169
00:14:52,450 --> 00:14:56,750
Damn that Bege guy! I'll make him pay!

170
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:03,500
Luffy, this is what I wanted to discuss with you.

171
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:10,720
I came up with a plan
 after I learned everything from Pekoms.

172
00:15:10,720 --> 00:15:13,390
I tried to predict your actions.

173
00:15:13,970 --> 00:15:16,310
I figured that if you learned the truth,

174
00:15:16,310 --> 00:15:21,150
you would decide to rescue Sanji and his family.

175
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:27,230
Perhaps it's not fair to Pekoms,
but considering the circumstances,

176
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:30,890
should we really
make an enemy of Bege?

177
00:15:34,620 --> 00:15:37,700
The tea party begins at 10 a.m.

178
00:15:37,700 --> 00:15:40,330
That's about five hours from now.

179
00:15:40,330 --> 00:15:44,130
The 10 of us need to come up
with a plan in that time frame.

180
00:15:44,130 --> 00:15:46,390
Stop counting us as a part of this!

181
00:15:46,390 --> 00:15:49,760
You damn brutes!
I'll let them know what you're up to!

182
00:15:49,760 --> 00:15:56,940
Listen, Luffy, Bege and his crew have been
 relentlessly preparing for this day.

183
00:16:00,020 --> 00:16:02,080
Luffy! Sanji!

184
00:16:02,820 --> 00:16:05,060
Let's ally with Bege!

185
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:07,070
What?!

186
00:16:11,530 --> 00:16:14,320
But... you're probably right.

187
00:16:14,320 --> 00:16:15,910
What?!

188
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:19,120
Hey, are you insane, Luffy?!

189
00:16:19,120 --> 00:16:21,100
Luffy wants to do this?!

190
00:16:21,100 --> 00:16:23,650
You see? I told you he would want to!

191
00:16:23,650 --> 00:16:26,960
Luffy, four of our six here are against this!

192
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:30,800
Don't you care about Bege-san's ill deeds?!

193
00:16:30,800 --> 00:16:33,880
Well, this way, everything'll work out, right?

194
00:16:33,880 --> 00:16:35,980
You can't make a decision like that...

195
00:16:35,980 --> 00:16:40,020
Actually, I arranged a meeting earlier.
Do you want to go meet them?

196
00:16:40,020 --> 00:16:42,020
Okay, let's go right now!

197
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:44,140
What?!

198
00:16:44,140 --> 00:16:48,040
Don't worry. If something
doesn't feel right, you can refuse!

199
00:16:48,040 --> 00:16:51,080
We have a different goal, after all.

200
00:16:52,110 --> 00:16:57,880
Luffy, Sanji! Bege and his crew's base
 is on the northwest side of the island.

201
00:16:57,880 --> 00:17:03,110
The eight of us will head there first
from this dimension. See you there!

202
00:17:03,110 --> 00:17:05,920
Stop counting us as part of your group!

203
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:08,090
Okay, got it!

204
00:17:20,880 --> 00:17:23,060
Did you get rid of Bobbin?

205
00:17:23,060 --> 00:17:26,440
That's right, he was chasing Black Leg.

206
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:30,180
I told you, Germa are my heroes.

207
00:17:33,320 --> 00:17:36,490
Are they really coming here?

208
00:17:37,120 --> 00:17:38,470
Father?

209
00:17:40,660 --> 00:17:44,710
Jinbe isn't the type of man to joke around.

210
00:17:45,260 --> 00:17:48,670
Since we're both opposing Big Mom,

211
00:17:48,670 --> 00:17:54,010
we shouldn't make extra enemies—
he's right about that.

212
00:17:54,010 --> 00:17:57,380
Everything after that depends on what Straw Hat says.

213
00:17:57,380 --> 00:18:00,100
If it doesn't work out...

214
00:18:01,770 --> 00:18:04,100
we'll just kill him!

215
00:18:27,830 --> 00:18:32,350
♪ Soft and fluffy... ♪

216
00:18:30,040 --> 00:18:32,350
♪ Moist and fluffy... ♪

217
00:18:32,350 --> 00:18:36,340
♪ ...life! ♪

218
00:18:34,840 --> 00:18:36,340
♪ There's no such thing! ♪

219
00:18:36,340 --> 00:18:42,470
♪ A life of torment, the taste of tears... ♪

220
00:18:42,470 --> 00:18:43,850
♪ A pinch of salt! ♪

221
00:18:43,850 --> 00:18:49,270
♪ Tears of mortification! ♪

222
00:18:46,960 --> 00:18:49,270
♪ A tablespoonful ♪

223
00:18:49,270 --> 00:18:54,150
♪ If that's how it is at least for your dessert... ♪

224
00:18:54,150 --> 00:19:04,030
♪ ...don't you want some sweet cake? ♪

225
00:18:58,820 --> 00:19:04,030
Head Chef! Head Chef!

226
00:19:04,030 --> 00:19:08,170
♪ Soft and fluffy... ♪

227
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:08,170
♪ Moist and fluffy... ♪

228
00:19:08,170 --> 00:19:11,920
♪ Soft and fluffy... ♪

229
00:19:10,170 --> 00:19:11,920
♪ Moist and fluffy... ♪

230
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:16,000
♪ Soft and fluffy... ♪

231
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:16,000
♪ Moist and fluffy... ♪

232
00:19:16,000 --> 00:19:20,450
♪ Soft and fluffy... ♪

233
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:20,450
♪ Moist and fluffy... ♪

234
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:30,770
No, Pekoms! You need to rest!

235
00:19:32,740 --> 00:19:40,320
Did Jinbe really tell Mama about that rat, Bege?

236
00:19:40,320 --> 00:19:41,740
Of course!

237
00:19:41,740 --> 00:19:48,160
By now, I'm guessing that Bege
has been beaten to death by Mama.

238
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:53,520
You guess?! Your guess isn't enough!
I gotta make sure to tell her...

239
00:19:53,520 --> 00:19:55,290
Whoa now!

240
00:19:58,040 --> 00:20:00,880
You need to keep resting, Pekoms.

241
00:20:00,880 --> 00:20:07,180
But, Praline, in case they stop him from telling her...

242
00:20:07,180 --> 00:20:10,690
If you're concerned about that,
then leaving it to Jinbe is the best option!

243
00:20:10,690 --> 00:20:15,310
You'll be beaten again in your current condition.
 Just keep quiet!

244
00:20:15,310 --> 00:20:19,810
He's right, Pekoms!
As a ship's doctor, I won't allow you to go!

245
00:20:19,810 --> 00:20:21,530
Don't move a muscle!

246
00:20:21,530 --> 00:20:22,950
He's right! He's right!

247
00:20:22,950 --> 00:20:24,870
– Yeah.
– Rest! Rest!

248
00:20:33,510 --> 00:20:36,710
You guys are acting weird.

249
00:20:36,710 --> 00:20:38,000
Gulp!

250
00:20:38,000 --> 00:20:42,390
There was something going on
last night in the inlet.

251
00:20:42,390 --> 00:20:46,390
I saw some people carrying things around!

252
00:20:46,390 --> 00:20:47,510
Gulp!

253
00:20:49,260 --> 00:20:53,640
I appreciate that you saved me,
but I need to leave!

254
00:20:53,640 --> 00:20:56,090
Wait, wait, we can't allow that!

255
00:20:56,090 --> 00:20:58,860
What do you mean you "can't"?

256
00:20:58,860 --> 00:21:01,340
What are you guys hiding?!

257
00:21:01,340 --> 00:21:03,800
Gulp!

258
00:21:15,290 --> 00:21:16,780
This is it!

259
00:21:16,780 --> 00:21:18,750
This is Bege's base!

260
00:21:30,450 --> 00:21:33,140
So, what kind of guy is Bege?

261
00:21:33,140 --> 00:21:35,480
You heard what Jinbe said.

262
00:21:36,810 --> 00:21:38,940
You coward!

263
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:49,030
Think of him as a scheming
and brutal mafia boss.

264
00:22:02,050 --> 00:22:06,450
My hero! Vinsmoke Sanji of Germa!

265
00:22:06,450 --> 00:22:09,190
I'm so happy to see you again-rero !

266
00:22:10,080 --> 00:22:11,100
It's you...

267
00:22:11,100 --> 00:22:14,140
Hey, where's everyone else?
Are you Bege?

268
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:18,650
Don't be in such a rush.
They are here or rero.

269
00:22:18,650 --> 00:22:20,360
What do you mean by "rero "?!

270
00:22:21,400 --> 00:22:24,650
Oh, Luffy! Sanji!

271
00:22:24,650 --> 00:22:26,700
Sanji!

272
00:22:26,700 --> 00:22:29,800
You made me worried, you bastard!

273
00:22:29,800 --> 00:22:31,950
I'm sorry for that... Hm?

274
00:22:32,840 --> 00:22:35,540
That aside, why are you dressed like this?

275
00:22:37,090 --> 00:22:40,350
Why don't you guys go take a bath too?

276
00:22:41,330 --> 00:22:46,090
Why are you so relaxed?! We don't have time!
And you don't even like baths!

277
00:22:46,090 --> 00:22:48,630
No, you two must take one, too-rero.

278
00:22:49,700 --> 00:22:52,350
We'll talk afterwards-rero.

279
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:54,470
A bath right now?!

280
00:22:54,470 --> 00:22:58,770
Father won't meet with anyone who is dirty.

281
00:22:58,770 --> 00:23:00,610
Who's dirty?!

282
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:25,500
What?! Lola was turned
 into a warthog zombie?!

283
00:23:25,500 --> 00:23:29,470
And she was chasing around
a guy she fell in love with!

284
00:23:29,470 --> 00:23:32,140
That definitely sounds like Lola!

285
00:23:32,140 --> 00:23:35,500
Back then... and now once again
in those scary woods,

286
00:23:35,500 --> 00:23:39,020
I don't know what would've happened to me
if it weren't for Lola.

287
00:23:39,020 --> 00:23:44,750
I see! But you guys saved my sister, too!
Thank you!

288
00:23:44,750 --> 00:23:47,360
Oh, I'm crying tears of joy.

289
00:23:47,360 --> 00:23:50,900
We've been close our entire lives.

290
00:23:51,820 --> 00:23:53,370
Since we're twins!

291
00:23:53,370 --> 00:23:58,660
A zombie! I can't imagine a dead person moving.
The sea is like a wonderland!

292
00:23:59,570 --> 00:24:02,370
So, was Lola turned back into a human?

293
00:24:02,370 --> 00:24:06,500
That's right. I'm sure she's
still doing well as a pirate.

294
00:24:11,340 --> 00:24:14,720
I wonder if she found someone to marry...

295
00:24:16,840 --> 00:24:22,770
Big Mom sounded so mad when she talked about
Lola running away from a marriage.

296
00:24:26,150 --> 00:24:29,900
Yeah... that was a big deal.

297
00:24:29,900 --> 00:24:30,860
What?

298
00:24:31,410 --> 00:24:35,990
Mama is reviled by all giants
in the world for a reason.

299
00:24:35,990 --> 00:24:39,200
All of the giants in the world?

300
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:43,800
That's why even though
Totto Land has a diverse population,

301
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:46,670
there are no giants.

302
00:24:46,670 --> 00:24:49,210
Giants really exist!

303
00:24:50,180 --> 00:24:51,400
One day,

304
00:24:52,700 --> 00:24:54,590
Lola had a surprise suitor

305
00:24:54,590 --> 00:24:58,260
who claimed it was love at first sight.

306
00:24:59,850 --> 00:25:04,770
It was none other than Prince Loki of Elbaf,
 the land of the giants!

307
00:25:04,770 --> 00:25:06,480
A prince?! Amazing!

308
00:25:07,860 --> 00:25:10,480
Mama practically cried with joy.

309
00:25:11,110 --> 00:25:13,990
She thought if Lola became
the princess of Elbaf,

310
00:25:13,990 --> 00:25:16,780
her long-standing feud with
the giants would be resolved,

311
00:25:17,610 --> 00:25:24,580
and she'd even gain access to the army of Elbaf,
the country known as the mightiest in the whole world.

312
00:25:24,580 --> 00:25:26,250
I see...

313
00:25:27,540 --> 00:25:30,480
So that's what she ran away from.

314
00:25:31,460 --> 00:25:33,920
It all went downhill from there.

315
00:25:35,430 --> 00:25:37,960
She tried to use me as a substitute,

316
00:25:38,720 --> 00:25:41,190
but he noticed that I wasn't Lola.

317
00:25:42,100 --> 00:25:46,230
So her relationship with the giants
got even worse.

318
00:25:47,500 --> 00:25:52,780
Then, she gave up the idea of
becoming friendly with actual giants

319
00:25:52,780 --> 00:25:56,660
and started investing in research
to gigantify regular humans instead.

320
00:25:57,660 --> 00:26:03,960
Her anger toward Lola only worsened,
and she was branded a criminal in this country!

321
00:26:03,960 --> 00:26:06,710
If she ever comes back, she'll be killed!

322
00:26:07,920 --> 00:26:13,300
Furthermore, she couldn't stand
looking at me anymore, since I look just like Lola.

323
00:26:13,300 --> 00:26:17,510
Get that damn face out of my sight!

324
00:26:18,000 --> 00:26:23,890
When she saw me, she hit me without mercy.
For years, I always had fresh wounds.

325
00:26:25,930 --> 00:26:28,950
I was afraid that my own mother would kill me!

326
00:26:30,500 --> 00:26:34,570
I can't see that monster
as my mother anymore!

327
00:26:38,450 --> 00:26:47,180
However, Lola is very carefree... She probably has no idea that her mother wants to kill her.

328
00:26:48,410 --> 00:26:51,920
I see... Everything makes sense now.

329
00:26:51,920 --> 00:26:58,550
So when Bege said he was going to assassinate Mama,
I felt nothing at all.

330
00:26:59,090 --> 00:27:02,810
You might think I'm terrible,
but it's the truth.

331
00:27:04,010 --> 00:27:06,800
Well, well, that bath felt so good!

332
00:27:08,890 --> 00:27:11,470
Ah, just like heaven!

333
00:27:11,470 --> 00:27:13,650
No, I refuse to move on to the next life!

334
00:27:14,770 --> 00:27:20,280
This feels like the aftermath of a battle...
I'm getting too relaxed. It hasn't even started yet!

335
00:27:22,990 --> 00:27:25,120
Luffy-san, Luffy-san.

336
00:27:25,120 --> 00:27:28,500
There's milk in here. Milk!

337
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:33,130
Hey, don't go through our fridge without asking!

338
00:27:33,130 --> 00:27:37,590
That's exactly what I needed.
I lost my tooth.

339
00:27:37,590 --> 00:27:41,220
And my face has been cracked.

340
00:27:41,220 --> 00:27:43,680
Thank you for the milk!

341
00:27:58,530 --> 00:28:00,700
All better!

342
00:28:00,700 --> 00:28:03,270
How is that even possible?!

343
00:28:03,980 --> 00:28:06,910
I won't forgive you, Chiffon!
I can't believe you!

344
00:28:06,910 --> 00:28:10,780
How can you help someone
who wants to kill Mama!

345
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:18,050
Mistress Chiffon, please think about this!
You know no one could ever kill Mama!

346
00:28:18,050 --> 00:28:19,920
Big Sis Brûlée!

347
00:28:19,920 --> 00:28:23,180
You know what she's done to me, right?

348
00:28:24,470 --> 00:28:29,520
I'm worried about Lola.
Bege and Pez are my only family now!

349
00:28:29,520 --> 00:28:31,210
I don't need anyone else!

350
00:28:32,740 --> 00:28:34,560
Oh, it's okay, it's okay.

351
00:28:42,360 --> 00:28:45,570
Okay, everyone's gathered, right?

352
00:28:45,570 --> 00:28:48,490
Have you cleaned yourselves up a bit?

353
00:28:49,490 --> 00:28:52,870
As the saying goes, "The suit makes the man."

354
00:28:52,870 --> 00:28:57,210
I won't talk to anyone that doesn't take care of their appearance.

355
00:29:01,750 --> 00:29:05,090
So, we've got three and a half hours to go.

356
00:29:05,720 --> 00:29:07,510
Let's first decide...

357
00:29:08,640 --> 00:29:12,560
if we're working together or not.

358
00:29:32,070 --> 00:29:33,620
They're good, aren't they, Luffy?

359
00:29:33,620 --> 00:29:36,170
Why don't you guys restrain yourselves?!

360
00:29:36,170 --> 00:29:39,250
What? These are for us to eat, right?

361
00:29:42,010 --> 00:29:45,800
From our perspective, you guys are just a nuisance.

362
00:29:47,390 --> 00:29:52,020
The easiest solution would be for us to kill all of you, here and now.

363
00:29:52,020 --> 00:29:53,520
Are you sure about that?

364
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:59,520
If I die, you won't have your chance to kill Big Mom.

365
00:30:00,300 --> 00:30:02,580
Because the ceremony would be canceled.

366
00:30:02,580 --> 00:30:06,860
If I'm not back two hours before the wedding,
they'll be suspicious.

367
00:30:06,860 --> 00:30:10,630
Yeah. I hate to admit it, but you're right.

368
00:30:10,630 --> 00:30:13,330
We'll keep you alive, in that case.

369
00:30:14,540 --> 00:30:17,170
We don't have time to waste on threats.

370
00:30:20,670 --> 00:30:24,800
Luffy, how are you feeling about this?
Can you work with them?

371
00:30:24,800 --> 00:30:26,010
What do you think?

372
00:30:45,990 --> 00:30:48,200
You're Caesar, aren't you?!

373
00:30:49,360 --> 00:30:52,690
What?! Caesar?! Where?!

374
00:30:52,690 --> 00:30:54,330
He's been here the whole time...

375
00:30:54,330 --> 00:30:56,250
How could you not notice...?

376
00:31:07,670 --> 00:31:12,930
This research is so pointless!
I'm not gonna work anymore!

377
00:31:12,930 --> 00:31:16,560
Go ahead and do as you like with me, Big Mom!

378
00:31:19,700 --> 00:31:21,600
Caesar Clown!

379
00:31:26,100 --> 00:31:30,280
I-I-I'm working my butt off!
Tell that to Big Mom!

380
00:31:30,280 --> 00:31:31,940
There's no need.

381
00:31:31,940 --> 00:31:32,950
What?

382
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:39,910
When I asked them to let me watch over you,
they agreed without a question.

383
00:31:39,910 --> 00:31:43,540
I'm now a trusted rook!

384
00:31:47,150 --> 00:31:49,250
Is that my heart?!

385
00:31:49,250 --> 00:31:54,140
I'm willing to let you go.
If you help me in return, that is...

386
00:31:55,350 --> 00:32:00,490
You bastard!
Do you have any idea who you're talking to?!

387
00:32:00,490 --> 00:32:05,360
I'm the genius scientist Caesar Clown! 
I could destroy the world if I wanted to!

388
00:32:12,030 --> 00:32:14,040
I know who you are.

389
00:32:14,040 --> 00:32:16,410
That's why I came here.

390
00:32:18,840 --> 00:32:20,370
Damn!

391
00:32:20,370 --> 00:32:23,330
I served Big Mom and now Bege!

392
00:32:23,330 --> 00:32:26,260
I gotta work anyway!

393
00:32:26,260 --> 00:32:28,340
Are you doing your job-rero ?

394
00:32:28,340 --> 00:32:31,590
I am! Who do you think I am?!

395
00:32:31,590 --> 00:32:35,260
This is much more to my liking
than what she had me do!

396
00:32:35,260 --> 00:32:40,010
The greatest piece of art
will soon be completed!

397
00:32:42,460 --> 00:32:44,480
That's good to know.

398
00:32:44,480 --> 00:32:48,480
The Straw Hat crew will be here shortly-rero.

399
00:32:48,480 --> 00:32:51,530
What?! The Straw Hats?!

400
00:32:51,530 --> 00:32:54,990
Oh, come on!
I never wanna see those guys again!

401
00:32:55,240 --> 00:32:59,400
When they're around,
everything goes wrong!

402
00:33:00,410 --> 00:33:05,470
Father wants you to attend the meeting too-rero.

403
00:33:05,470 --> 00:33:07,960
Don't be late.

404
00:33:12,170 --> 00:33:14,380
I can't believe this!

405
00:33:14,380 --> 00:33:16,430
I've got no choice!

406
00:33:21,390 --> 00:33:27,150
C-Caesar?
No, I am Bege's blood brother...

407
00:33:28,040 --> 00:33:30,530
"Gangster" Gastino!

408
00:33:34,980 --> 00:33:38,870
He's not even attempting to hide it...

409
00:33:37,410 --> 00:33:38,870
"Gastino"?

410
00:33:39,360 --> 00:33:40,740
Because he's a gas human?

411
00:33:40,740 --> 00:33:43,040
He's even laughing the same way.

412
00:33:43,040 --> 00:33:46,070
I see.  I thought you were
someone else. Sorry about that.

413
00:33:46,070 --> 00:33:49,360
No, you were right!
He's obviously Caesar!

414
00:33:49,360 --> 00:33:50,170
What?!

415
00:33:50,170 --> 00:33:53,750
Oh, so it is you!
What are you doing here?!

416
00:33:53,750 --> 00:33:57,050
Do you really think I'd be here
if I had a choice, you idiot?!

417
00:33:57,050 --> 00:34:00,680
Because of you guys,
I was handed over to Big Mom,

418
00:34:00,680 --> 00:34:05,430
and my only escape from certain death was
 this guy taking my heart and making me his slave!

419
00:34:05,430 --> 00:34:06,890
I'm being pushed around!

420
00:34:07,870 --> 00:34:12,280
If you see Trafalgar Law, tell him I'll kill him when I see him again!

421
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:14,190
You too, if I get the chance!

422
00:34:14,190 --> 00:34:17,110
Cut it out! This is so pointless.

423
00:34:23,330 --> 00:34:26,120
What a waste of time.

424
00:34:26,120 --> 00:34:28,550
Straw Hat,

425
00:34:28,550 --> 00:34:31,710
are you going to work with me or not?

426
00:34:39,940 --> 00:34:43,100
First of all, let me punch you for shooting Pekoms!

427
00:34:47,690 --> 00:34:48,520
Here I go!

428
00:34:53,050 --> 00:34:54,530
Stop it!

429
00:34:56,820 --> 00:34:58,030
What?!

430
00:35:01,450 --> 00:35:06,290
Pull back your fist, Luffy!
We won't come to an agreement this way!

431
00:35:06,290 --> 00:35:08,960
But he shot my friend!

432
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:13,100
Anyone talking bad about Father is unforgivable!

433
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:14,920
No, Gotti! Calm down-rero !

434
00:35:14,920 --> 00:35:16,050
Cut it out!

435
00:35:16,050 --> 00:35:17,670
I don't care. Let him do it.

436
00:35:19,590 --> 00:35:21,760
Kick these bastards out!

437
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:23,390
You back off!

438
00:35:25,280 --> 00:35:27,520
Why?!

439
00:35:29,020 --> 00:35:30,900
I knew this would happen...

440
00:35:30,900 --> 00:35:33,230
Well, it can't be helped...

441
00:35:35,130 --> 00:35:36,940
Do you like Big Mom?

442
00:35:37,920 --> 00:35:39,400
– No way!
– No way!
– No way!

443
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:42,540
Then you're on the same side.

444
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:47,910
Even if you don't share the same lifestyle or goals,
you have a common enemy!

445
00:35:49,000 --> 00:35:52,080
You can kill each other later,

446
00:35:52,080 --> 00:35:56,130
but if you join hands now,
it'll be in everyone's favor!

447
00:35:59,420 --> 00:36:00,870
So what's the plan?!

448
00:36:00,870 --> 00:36:03,520
I've planned the whole thing in exacting detail.

449
00:36:03,520 --> 00:36:07,680
Let's just do it!
Then, I'll be through with you guys!

